Feature: Contact Us Form

  Scenario: Submit Contact Us Form - valid data
    Given I am on the contact us page
    When I complete all fields
    And I click the submit button
    Then the form is successfully completed


  Scenario: Log in BBC invalid credentials
    Given I am on the BBC page
    When I click the sign in button
    And I complete email and password with invalid data
    And I click submit
    Then an error message is displayed
